
              THE OCAMLTTER TWITTER CLIENT
              ============================

REQUIREMENT
===========
	
	You need:

	    - Objective Caml
	      (available at http://caml.inria.fr/)
       

INSTALLATION
============

        Nothing to do.


HOW TO USE
==========

        1. Run

           $ ./ocamltter

        2. You can use following commands:

           - l();;             list timeline
           - l ~c:COUNT();;    list timeline
           - lc COUNT;;        list timeline
           - l ~u:"NAME"();;   list NAME's timeline
           - lu "NAME";;       list NAME's timeline
           - u "TEXT";;        post a new message
           - re ID "TEXT";;    reply to ID
           - rt ID;;           retweet ID
           - qt ID "TEXT";;    qt ID
           - s "WORD";;        search by a WORD
           - login NAME;;      login
           - let CMD = ...;;   define a your own command CMD
           - help;;            print a list of commands
	   
        3. You may modify the config.ml
           - You can set your twitter id

        4. Quit

            #quit;;  or  ^D


BUGS REPORT
===========

        Send your bug reports at

          y.imai at ocaml.jp

	